query.selectQuery: SELECT transform("eiel_c_abast_ca"."GEOMETRY", ?T) AS "GEOMETRY", "eiel_c_abast_ca"."id", "eiel_c_abast_ca"."id_municipio", (select getnucleo_ca(eiel_c_abast_ca.id_municipio, eiel_c_abast_ca.orden_ca, eiel_c_abast_ca.clave)) as nombre_oficial, eiel_t_abast_ca."nombre" AS nombre, eiel_t_abast_ca."orden_ca" AS orden_ca, eiel_t_abast_ca."tipo" AS tipo, eiel_t_abast_ca."sist_impulsion" AS sist_impulsion, eiel_t_abast_ca."estado" AS estado, eiel_t_abast_ca."uso" AS uso, eiel_t_abast_ca."proteccion" AS proteccion, eiel_t_abast_ca."contador" AS contador FROM "eiel_c_abast_ca" LEFT JOIN "public"."eiel_t_abast_ca" eiel_t_abast_ca ON eiel_c_abast_ca."clave" = eiel_t_abast_ca."clave" AND eiel_c_abast_ca."codmunic" = eiel_t_abast_ca."codmunic" AND eiel_c_abast_ca."orden_ca" = eiel_t_abast_ca."orden_ca" AND eiel_c_abast_ca."codprov" = eiel_t_abast_ca."codprov" WHERE "eiel_c_abast_ca"."id_municipio" IN (?M) and (eiel_c_abast_ca.revision_expirada=9999999999 AND eiel_t_abast_ca.revision_expirada=9999999999)
